.TH LANGPACK-INSPECTOR 1 "2026-02-15" "Daniel Nylander" "Language Pack Inspector Manual"
.SH NAME
langpack-inspector - Inspect Ubuntu language pack coverage
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B langpack-inspector
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBlangpack-inspector\fR is a GTK4/Adwaita application for inspecting Ubuntu language pack coverage and .mo files. It lists installed language packs, shows included .mo files per package, compares with available Launchpad templates, displays translated/untranslated string counts, flags outdated translations, and provides direct Launchpad links.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/langpack-inspector/
Configuration files.
.TP
.I ~/.cache/langpack-inspector/
Cached data.
